        "article": "In the ICC Women&#8217;s T20 World Cup, England will take on Australia in the final at Lord&#8217;s Cricket Ground in London today. Both teams head into the title clash unbeaten. Australia secured their place in the final with a victory over the West Indies in the semi-finals, while England defeated South Africa on Thursday to register their sixth consecutive win and book a place in the championship decider.",
